o]]\n| \n|-\n| 1994\n| ''[[No Man's Land (play)|No Man's Land]]''\n| Spooner\n| \n|-\n| 1997\n| ''[[Barrymore (play)|Barrymore]]''\n| [[John Barrymore]]\n| \n|-\n| 2004\n| ''[[King Lear]]''\n|[[Leir of Britain|King Lear]]\n| \n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Inherit the Wind (play)|Inherit the Wind]]''\n| Henry Drummond\n| \n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Voice role\n! Notes\n|-\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Star Trek: Klingon Academy]]''\n| [[Chang (Star Trek)|General Chang]]\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[Up (video game)|Up]]''\n| Charles Muntz (voice)\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim]]''\n| Arngeir (voice)\n|<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[The Long Dark]]''\n| Narrator\n|\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==References==\n{{refbegin}}\n*{{Cite web\n  | url = https://www.allmovie.com/artist/christopher-plummer-p57110\n  | title = Christopher Plummer - Filmography\n  | publisher = [[Allmovie]]\n  | accessdate = July 16, 2017}}\n*{{Cite web\n  | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/christopher_plummer/\n  | title = Christopher Plummer on Rotten Tomatoes\n  | publisher = [[Rotten Tomatoes]]\n  | accessdate = November 19, 2017}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.allmovie.com/artist/christopher-plummer-p57110 Christopher Plummer] at [[Allmovie]]\n*{{IMDb name|id=0001626|name=Christopher Plummer}}\n*{{IBDB name|id=56307|name=Christopher Plummer}}\n*[https://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/christopher_plummer/ Christopher Plummer] at [[Rotten Tomatoes]]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Plummer, Christopher, Filmography}}\n[[Category:Male actor filmographies]]\n[[Category:American filmographies]]\n[[Category:Canadian filmographies]]\n", "name_user": "Moe1810", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eTelevision", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Plummer_filmography"}
